<HEAD>Magazine Names USDA Facility in N.D. as Laboratory of the Year</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Agriculture Department said Thursday its
new Northern Crop Science Laboratory in Fargo, N.D., has been named
as ``laboratory of the year'' by Research &amp; Development magazine.
   R. Dean Plowman, administrator of the department's Agricultural
