prosecutor who has likened me to Adolf Hitler, we now face many
months and perhaps years of fighting the remaining charges.
Nonetheless, we are absolutely confident of the final outcome. As a
Marine, I was taught to fight and fight hard, for as long as it
takes to prevail. We will continue this battle and with the support
and prayers of the American people, we will be fully vindicated.''
